pageContext.description: One edge badly damaged near the point. Mid rib extending up to point round in section. Ribs on wings of blade, running parallel to the edges, and curving inwards to meet the socket at right-angles. Stump of wooden shaft in socket. Casting flaw in side of socket.
pageContext.patina: One side is a uniform khaki-coloured; the other rather browner, with patches of black; black round orifice of socket.
